    summary: "Aporro is a global streetwear and hip-hop jewelry brand that specializes in \"iced out\" chains, pendants, and other accessories. Their designs often fuse hip-hop culture with intricate details and precise stone settings to create bold and individualistic pieces[1][2].\n\nKey aspects of Aporro\'s jewelry include:\n*   **Product Range** Aporro offers a variety of hip-hop jewelry, including Cuban chains, rope chains, tennis chains, and various pendants. They also sell bracelets, rings, and custom grillz[3][1][2][4][5][6]. Popular pendant designs include the \"Aporro A\302\256\"[3][7][8][9], \"Graffiti Jesus\"[10][11], \"Shield\"[12], and \"Hamsa\"[13] styles, with options for custom lettering and logos[1][4][14].\n*   **Materials and Craftsmanship** The jewelry is typically made from brass or 925 sterling silver, with finishes like 14K or white gold plating[7][12][8][10][14][6]. The \"iced out\" effect is achieved using stones such as Cubic Zirconia (CZ) and Moissanite[7][12][8][10][14][6]. Aporro states that their Moissanite passes standard diamond testers[11]. They emphasize meticulous handcrafting and solid construction with precise stone setting for durability and brilliance[1].\n*   **Design Philosophy** Aporro aims to provide jewelry that embodies individuality and attitude by blending traditional craftsmanship with street culture and modern trends[1][2]. They are noted for their unique and flashy designs[15].\n*   **Customization Options** Aporro provides custom jewelry services, allowing customers to personalize pendants with names, letters, or specific designs[1][4][14]. They also offer free clasp customization for Cuban chains, enabling personalized details like logos or names[16].\n*   **Customer Experience** Aporro offers a 365-day guarantee on eligible purchases and provides detailed packaging. They facilitate worldwide shipping and offer flexible payment plans[3][15][14][11]. However, some reviews suggest that while the presentation is luxurious, the value for money, particularly for plated items, might be questionable compared to solid gold or sterling silver options from other brands[15][17]. Returns are generally not accepted for solid gold or custom/made-to-order products once production has commenced[3][16].\n\nSources:\n[1] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH-FToTz9Q33B_TA_mirNCjFwNRuqbxs7Wy-yp9ajNawFz_OUNuTmDKuxKvj8HhWqrdxjTFONwiVm06I-pUSpMubqXn71j5lcG9jmq5z-n78AvwlNFOlDm0I3ZzmXdPebKbJ-Yg95MPl6baLPd6af2StbpAMA6jN8LT-e6k4g==)\n[2] [aporro.shop](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHXJDVN5OZAzjZyeTzZCwtYIx1Jf6qDFa-d3np4sOyAvqmd6GPA71S8ndqYWpuF1uefce97zCOWCa6vtUksF9RYNJIDycaV1gcLXREjN4XY)\n[3] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEt_iqVEsCQ-ret04YBGXf1A6Yf3FNd0nSuiWeggsNppc6WWC0TEUL2kIpb0WJSw3GqYB5k_o4CUrRE5_nWN36V2GYZSnfx4-Revg4U-4yk6FAOyRMl8ITb1Pp0QzzyidzMbM98KVnZQIesekLwqja0WY7v6O8=)\n[4] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF6XD0ym7PZOa89c4h0bPB3vysER9j6k4oRPt6w1djDi-tCS-4QVj-eiNw5sTxOreMPJBRXvdR-u46lQArQ967yCXXt_y9BnVaur30MOHXMa3aCI2LmzyOpAtf_RtKVa9k26VvRpZ395rd8SiFGpcLXhqxVRcskSniUSzo=)\n[5] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENhMSVmjzrxNgv81qxl9j-_BNUD1hw9JIJhoGXydfwCnKrqZ4di_Ae47T2_9Btmbh44m-mC2dO-xtRdTUvwsDOKSnvVnMqRgqs_r7F8MypRjneq5P41nMpsiZ8ki0g1o7NabLoZ9cQrUxN9aVqAQE1lR3OmjL9nbDD2y8TZBC_MYG19IAjTR8tSQ==)\n[6] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG9fRaAqKZtPL3IZaPUDG5o3w1oL2_2OGOD7a-bA10w1vxXlp0Xngx9U8X2cz0cdXwimezGmjKb-gd39FN5HBn_V-ANH9Sfb3bl-HUCZLGNOaJapn2M5lPf-BTSc30jaPPwLMX1PlaVKzUW4kLEH9E=)\n[7] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHDGJnmjY5bNR0bR-pbMbWweS31hsqQxnA7LtumkLCKt7nloEqEL24DnZ5aQQYorajjfbvBlULtmxOWWM7AKAEHXn5gsZ49-XnlC_khpE1lz5EPAZNzVB1fYvBoCABXYICfbNgXHHLF6EuH097m4lvRr