      title: "aporro.com"
    }
    summary: "Aporro is a brand specializing in hip-hop and streetwear jewelry, offering a wide array of collections and specific jewelry types, including Cuban links, tennis chains, and grillz.[1]\n\nTheir offerings include:\n*   **Collections** Aporro features various collections, including \"Exclusive Collections\" and themed pieces that incorporate ancient symbolism with modern street culture, such as their Dragon and Ankh sets.[2][3] They also offer \"Best Deals\" and \"New Arrivals\" within their collections.[3]\n*   **Cuban Link Chains** Aporro provides a selection of Cuban link chains for men and women, often \"iced out\" with stones. These are available in various widths, such as 12mm, and materials like brass, 925 sterling silver, and with different gold platings (yellow, white, and rose gold).[4][5][6][7][8][3] They can be customized and feature details like iced-out box clasps.[4][8]\n*   **Tennis Chains** The brand offers tennis chains, including iced versions, in different sizes and materials. These can feature 5A CZ stones or VVS Moissanite diamonds, set in brass or 925 sterling silver with gold plating.[9][10][11][12][13] Styles include classic iced tennis chains and those with unique arrangements of stones like emerald-cut and marquise-cut.[10]\n*   **Grillz** Aporro specializes in grillz, offering both pre-made and premium custom iced-out options.[14][15][16] Customers can choose from materials like 925 sterling silver, with various gold platings (yellow, white, and rose gold), and stone types such as cubic zirconia (CZ) or Moissanite.[15][17][18] Customization allows for unique designs, including iced-out letters, multi-color gemstones, and specific tooth counts.[14][17][18]\n\nSources:\n[1] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH-WSOw31pz6VfSoLX0trc05GiY1gZz_64ReT_mpM6SZXMHiCeZFYLutSvZHJBn0HRl_cpbiOnwLNg9LSzPctvQsrm9_hNgrwqUrBNYg4zWM7jy)\n[2] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG16eZTfGK9xayY5oqgmnifdur4dy_fSTVzb5m_ylTz1aHPggNdA-ez4gUlxhowUSqBWYAl1aaOaTy_FsvNG2CDEzhPAD6Z0imx9XHF7zqyesvtKtdUEAwIOeTqiTmrAbiqsAzaVs08aSFJrd9nyDSX)\n[3] [aporro.shop](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9_Wr-vw8YC-NrZnEGEX6ChBxYFhj5ao-QwAkJYo_PLCV364ekag-RpPp3LiFmwEsnEAu0JzmToVsZQysUntU6jkTSie5sCnFzdkrJih2G)\n[4] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFM3JsHPx67UtQP3iZGaqyoe5IFLWMQuRN7OOfi2Bhu1JmRJ5NCT99gyRbNjLotDjq5dB94ibsCK7zs1R4xib6ktair9oQCy9_IaVc7NwYTGfEQKptGvDptW96z67i-JjGgApbGFE5QuOggebTLp4SMvKCmG1xWT035Up8=)\n[5] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH3jmM8sAiuwryszSlEfI3ciuAAqKzwuj7MfqGuwOQ-YhW_6xt4JUi793tyYuNu3DN8-SyI2NUMdfDCXKJpDGGlno_XLs1lVQ-ejOx3hMohPgtMtf5E0Jgz1SuwfNO3-arOJBcO48x0tXTX3MG2sfUDHiWLvrgt14KuYPT93JMIW5QrOAQf5PuFlM9c)\n[6] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZ65VK8y8bcKsBycRhpDj-Y_FbUUWAGTuNSN92Kt8vxRruEE_j2vhecGtiERR5Vt36uQMvUMmWORrrdFFMCIT5nczz8du0uTlLJ6D3k9RQe_ebIb4_3kacQOnU04ej6mbc71w2gndzdaqNX7LKB7BEmJ_LjHE5FniuiBr6-QBxXg==)\n[7] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGvKAaezYHZRybERvM1FqP3xWYpaX_ACnMp888bJI8ZZaQInHK0P_6JFOLN_5cfq0zg6CUx7OjEsEFakj3VY1SdoyStItssh6xydQnHSCXQWX_LlSgjcjwoJeYlInaDQBYjkF5z71wj-cifPdWkd6anadkqCBmk736ZpA==)\n[8] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFlINddwV7z8yk9gfZd6WRQivU0KG0irkRFYKR2ZZDEZHV6N_xGmI9TsdywSYwib3zMgTZpiuhQnp7f3jomv0_D8QYvdcxJV5kKUhPxQGQFz1wvQHjL3tBTdxlHwFCluf6F00KB-5ASCinyyTLceOA=)\n[9] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHM3VVPil_YoB66DDsVp5f3FaQabL5tqymTP59z-D6FyXI-EsPsYMdgfQoAMgIZHM62E65vBiAz5B9K9pIFsQc9bpY5niRgt8chkw-r4wVl5mbdSxugRG47A_ie-h7mtkZmvGr1EHjnplUnQzrtkSMQDKGvr2Y0)\n[10] [aporro.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEP7q7RgoM